01:04:47.799 --> 01:04:50.710
[Matt]: Yes. So that's why I mentioned exercise,
which is that I think...

01:04:50.710 --> 01:04:52.009
[Rhonda]: Wow, that's so fascinating.

01:04:52.009 --> 01:04:55.710
[Matt]: So now we're all starting to sort
of, you know, realize how the sleep system

01:04:55.710 --> 01:05:01.079
is augmented, one of those paths, you know,
is light. The other is darkness. The other

01:05:01.079 --> 01:05:07.089
is temperature. But here's a fourth one. The
immune system. And we know that you can inject,

01:05:07.089 --> 01:05:12.250
you know, some of these cytokines into animals,
and you can almost induce sleep. It's that

01:05:12.250 --> 01:05:13.250
powerful.

01:05:13.250 --> 01:05:14.250
[Rhonda]: That's so cool.

