01:16:31.640 --> 01:16:36.270
when he was in medical residency, and you
see this in residence, too, you know, sickness

01:16:36.270 --> 01:16:42.120
rates, you know, increased dramatically. There
is weight gain, the diabetic profile, you

01:16:42.120 --> 01:16:47.900
know, in terms of their ability to manage
glucose becomes markedly impaired. We know

01:16:47.900 --> 01:16:52.800
that testosterone in men plummets when sleep
