[Matt]: Which, in other words, a lack of sleep
will age men by a decade in terms of that

01:17:02.690 --> 01:17:04.450
aspect of virility and wellness.

01:17:04.450 --> 01:17:06.880
[Rhonda]: How quickly does that happen? Do
you know? Is that like...?

01:17:06.880 --> 01:17:10.690
[Matt]: So you can see that within almost
days once you start to dose people on that.

01:17:10.690 --> 01:17:16.940
It comes about quite rapidly. You can see
hormonal change. I mean, I think that's what...if

01:17:16.940 --> 01:17:22.800
there is a major access...oh, sorry, axis
within the body that is altered by sleep it

01:17:22.800 --> 01:17:28.650
is the hormonal axis. I think that principally,
through the root of the autonomic nervous

01:17:28.650 --> 01:17:34.270
system, that is the lens through which almost
all sleep and sleep deprivation effects can

01:17:34.270 --> 01:17:35.270
