You know, I am on a mission. I'm desperately
trying to reach the public because I think

02:36:26.710 --> 02:36:32.869
this this message has been the neglected stepsister
in the health conversation of today. But I

02:36:32.869 --> 02:36:37.050
can't do it alone. I need to partner with,
you know, fantastic scientists and public

02:36:37.050 --> 02:36:42.070
figures, people like yourself who, you know,
provide this platform and this forum. So I'm

02:36:42.070 --> 02:36:46.979
going to anoint you as a sleep ambassador
now as well. So thank you. But just generally,

02:36:46.979 --> 02:36:51.210
thank you for this opportunity to reach your
audience and speak about sleep. I really do

02:36:51.210 --> 02:36:53.209
appreciate it so much.

